Faculty profile




Qi Alfred  ChenAssistant ProfessorDEGREE:Ph.D.RESEARCH AREAS: Security and PrivacyRESEARCH INTERESTS: Software and AI security, systems security, and network security. Currently, his research focuses on security problems at the AI and software stacks in autonomous CPS/IoT systems (e.g., autonomous driving, intelligent transportation, smart home).
CONTACT INFORMATION:

